text:
That was amazing!!!
The run just now... was super awesome!!!

It was really good but~~~
Sorry, can we try it again...!

I want to exude more of, like, a refreshing atmosphere!
It's like bursting with youthfulness, desperately fun...!

That's the vibe! You understand it, right,
Madoka-chan, right in the midst of youth...!?

Ah, yes...
Youthfulness, indeed... More youthfulness...

That's it!! More youthfulness!!
...Take 5, let's try it again~~~!

You... you can do it... Madoka...
I can only cheer you on... sorry...
